node.text: @artisansdegeneve introducing the new series “Meet the Passion” and today met and interviewed John Demsey, Executive Group President of Estee Lauder,  he opens up about his  passion for fine art, customization and watchmaking

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by 🇮🇹 L'avvocato 🇮🇹 on September 06, 2021 tagging @jacobandco, and @vertigo1983.

node.text:
The all new @jacobandco’s impressive Chiron Tourbillon in 7 different gemstones iterations.
This watch took almost 1 year to develop and it consists of 578 components.
The Chiron Tourbillon skills feature a case that houses a very complicated movement with a 1-minute 30° inclined flying tourbillon, the ”W16 Engine” in a sapphire block and a Power Reserve indicator. The addition of gemstones are the cherry on the top and give a touch of unmistakable flair👨‍🎨
A true engine on the wrist.

node.text:
Black Friday with the new all black Seamaster Diver 300M Black Black 💣 
Full ceramic case and bezel are finished with a grained relief ceramic bezel insert. Even the dial is made of ceramic with laser-etched waves and logo.
•
📸 @monochromewatches
